    "en": {
      "title": "Three people who set fire to the President's house were arrested",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the police, three suspects were arrested in connection with the incident of breaking into and setting fire to President Ranil Wickramasinghe's residence in Kollupitiya.",
        "This arrest has been made in Piliyanda and Narahenpita police domains during the night of yesterday (01). The arrested suspects are aged 18 and 22 and are residents of Madapata and Colombo 05 areas.",
        "The Criminal Investigation Department has arrested these suspects in connection with the investigation in this regard."
      ],
